<subSubSection pageId="49" pageNumber="50" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Shell sculptured with dense spiral lines, colour pattern predominantly with three small spiral bands of dark reddish-brown interrupted with white &lt;&lt; marks, aperture with a small dark band behind the lip, around the columellar margin, and on the parietal wall.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
